****************BREECH***************
This ability allows you to put some of
your lifeforce into your weapon. It is
a taxing ability so you will be tired 
after. You weapon will now hit things 
that would normally need enchanted 
weapons to hit, The bonus depends on
level, You recieve a +1 at level 10, a
+2 at level 20, a +3 at level 30, and
+4 at level 40.
The + lasts as long as your gun is held.

Level Obtained: Special
***************************************
